<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="明律" xml:id="gsz0806a07shiBianCai"><lb
n="0806a07" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0806a07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>朔方龍興寺<persName key="A011240">辯才</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0806a08"/><persName key="A011240">釋辯才</persName>，姓李氏，<placeName key="PL000000027119">襄陽</placeName>人也。母氏妊之，倏惡<lb
ed="T" n="0806a09"/>葷血，冥然一食，虛淡終辰。及其誕彌，異香<lb
ed="T" n="0806a10"/>盈室，宗黨怪焉。<date key="j19876871988051" from-iso="+0730-01-01" to-iso="+0730-12-31">七歲</date>依<placeName key="PL000000027106">峴山</placeName><persName key="A011241">寂禪師</persName>出家，<lb
ed="T" n="0806a11"/>厥長者明記：每受經法，必以等身為限。字<lb
ed="T" n="0806a12"/>不重問，義不再思，<persName key="A011241">師</persName>甚器之。<date key="j19909741991338" from-iso="+0739-01-01" to-iso="+0739-12-31">年十六</date>，遂削<lb
ed="T" n="0806a13"/>髮，隷本州<placeName key="PL000000027107">大雲寺</placeName>。次乃周遊列郡，登陟名<lb
ed="T" n="0806a14"/>山，就荊州<placeName key="PL000000027023">玉泉寺</placeName>納具戒。聞長安<placeName key="PL000000042180">安國寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0806a15"/><persName key="A011242">懷威律師</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042225">報恩寺</placeName><persName key="A011243">義頒律師</persName>，法門具瞻，師資表<lb
ed="T" n="0806a16"/>率，遂伏膺請業。有疑必決，無義不通，廁<lb
ed="T" n="0806a17"/>于二宗，推為上首。<date from-iso="+0755-02-20" key="j19968681997221" to-iso="+0756-02-08"><name>天寶</name>十四載</date>，<persName key="A000291">玄宗</persName>以北<lb
ed="T" n="0806a18"/>方人也，稟剛氣，多訛風，列剎之中，餘習騎<lb
ed="T" n="0806a19"/>射，有教無類，何可止息。詔以<persName key="A011240">才</persName>為教誡，臨<lb
ed="T" n="0806a20"/>壇度人。<date notBefore-iso="+0756-08-16" key="j19974111997556" notAfter-iso="+0757-01-08"><name>至德</name>初</date>，<persName key="A004378">肅宗</persName>即位是邦也。宰臣<persName key="A008503">杜<lb
ed="T" n="0806a21"/>鴻漸</persName>奏<persName key="A011240">才</persName>住龍興寺<!--找不到此地-->，詔加朔方管內教授大<lb
ed="T" n="0806a22"/>德。俾其訓勵，革獫狁之風，循毘尼之道。復<lb
ed="T" n="0806a23"/>命為國建法華道場<!--找不到此地-->。及駕迴，既復<placeName key="PLG00000000013">兩京</placeName>，累<lb
ed="T" n="0806a24"/>降璽書，末塗尤於大乘頓教留心。<date from-iso="+0766-02-18" key="j20008842001190" to-iso="+0766-12-21"><name>永泰</name>二<lb
ed="T" n="0806a25"/>年</date>，賊臣<persName key="A011283">僕固懷恩</persName>外招誘蕃戎，內贔金革。<lb
ed="T" n="0806a26"/><persName key="A011240">才</persName>勸勉毳裘，不誅華族。<date from-iso="+0768-01-28" key="j20015932001976" to-iso="+0769-02-14"><name>大曆</name>三載</date>追入充<lb
ed="T" n="0806a27"/><placeName key="PL000000042180">章信寺</placeName>大德。時府帥<anchor xml:id="beg0806001"/>虢<anchor xml:id="end0806001"/>國<persName key="A011285">常公</persName>素仰<persName key="A011240">才</persName>名，<lb
ed="T" n="0806a28"/>與護戎<persName key="A011286">任公</persName>，時親道論。<date from-iso="+0778-02-06" key="j20052552005608" to-iso="+0779-01-25">十三年</date>冬，現身有<lb
ed="T" n="0806a29"/>疾，至<date key="j20055872005587" when-iso="+0779-01-04">暮冬八日</date>，垂誡門徒已，安坐繩床，<pb ed="T" n="0806b" xml:id="T50.2061.0806b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0806b01"/>默然歸滅，春秋五十六。越<date from-iso="+0779-02-25" key="j20056392005668" to-iso="+0779-03-26">已未歲二月</date>遷神<lb
ed="T" n="0806b02"/>於寺<!--找不到此地-->內西北隅。先是有邑子石顒從役于<lb
ed="T" n="0806b03"/>城上，其夜未渠，聞管絃之聲自西至，乃天<lb
ed="T" n="0806b04"/>樂也。異香從空散下，則生淨方之兆也。<persName key="A011240">才</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0806b05"/>自<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>而旋于塞上，既受<persName key="A011285"><anchor xml:id="begd1e26692"/>虢<anchor xml:id="endd1e26692"/>公</persName>知遇，大<lb
ed="T" n="0806b06"/>營福業，成此精廬，皆<persName key="A011240">才</persName>之敦勸矣。勅諡大<lb
ed="T" n="0806b07"/>師曰<persName key="A011240">能覺</persName>，仍賜紫衣一副，追遠之榮，聲聞<lb
ed="T" n="0806b08"/><placeName key="PL000000000129">塞外</placeName>。<date notBefore-iso="+0901-05-18" key="j20502812051391" notAfter-iso="+0904-06-01"><name>天復</name>中</date><anchor xml:id="beg0806002"/>廷<anchor xml:id="end0806002"/>尉評<persName key="A011245">王儋</persName>為碑頌德云。</p>
